channel.title: SRL include
channel.description:
I hadn't used scar for a while but now that Aryan is dead I'm trying again. I've downloaded a SRL include I've found here. (Apparently the SRL forums are semi-private now and don't have a link). However, functions such as LoggedIn(), or LoginPlayer() dont work. LoggedIn always return another color than the one that is set. LoginPlayer() doesn't hit the last red "play" button.
My RS config is set to low quality, very bright. I am using Version 1 of SRL.
Is there any new SRL version that might be causing the trouble or something? If so could anyone post a link to download? Thank you.
